{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_vrtx_01W3G1NpcoSA56UxU3PUZ8F5","type":"tool_result","content":"The file /Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.prizmkit/specs/022-web-chat-input-placeholder-update/context-snapshot.md has been updated successfully."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"6c440504-ebad-473c-a26c-41e0ba2b264c","uuid":"8e3c800c-7b72-4a22-ae3b-7c9113583b56","timestamp":"2026-03-22T15:14:27.480Z","tool_use_result":{"filePath":"/Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.prizmkit/specs/022-web-chat-input-placeholder-update/context-snapshot.md","oldString":"## Section 5 — Existing Tests\n\nNo tests exist for HTML placeholder values (frontend-only static attribute change).","newString":"## Section 5 — Existing Tests\n\nNo tests exist for HTML placeholder values (frontend-only static attribute change).\n\n## Implementation Log\nFiles changed/created: public/index.html\nKey decisions: Single attribute change on textarea#chatInput, from「输入消息，支持 Shift+Enter 换行」to「请输入对话」. No backend, JS, or CSS changes needed. Pre-existing test failures (92) confirmed unrelated to this change.","originalFile":"# Context Snapshot — F-022: Web Chat Input Placeholder Update\n\n## Section 1 — Feature Brief\n\n**Description**: 将 Web 管理台聊天输入框的 placeholder 文本更新为「请输入对话」，提升界面可读性和用户引导性。修改范围限于 public/index.html 中 chatInput textarea 元素的 placeholder 属性，无后端变更。\n\n**Acceptance Criteria**:\n- Given 用户打开 Web 管理台, When 聊天输入框为空, Then 显示 placeholder 文字「请输入对话」\n- Given 用户在输入框中输入内容, When 输入框非空, Then placeholder 文字不再显示\n- Given 页面通过任意浏览器加载, When 渲染聊天输入框, Then placeholder 文字正确显示且无乱码\n\n## Section 2 — Project Structure\n\n- `public/index.html` — Web admin UI (87 lines)\n- `public/styles.css` — Stylesheet\n- `public/js/main.js` — Frontend JS module\n- `src/` — Backend Node.js/Express source\n\n## Section 3 — Prizm Context\n\nroot.prizm: PrizmClaw Node.js project, Express + Telegraf stack.\nNo L1/L2 docs needed — change is frontend HTML only, no backend or service changes.\n\n## Section 4 — Existing Source Files\n\n### public/index.html (87 lines)\n\n```html\n<!doctype html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n  <head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\" />\n    <title>PrizmClaw 管理台</title>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"./styles.css\" />\n  </head>\n  <body>\n    <div class=\"app-shell\">\n      <header class=\"app-header\">\n        <div>\n          <h1>PrizmClaw 管理台</h1>\n          <p class=\"subtitle\">聊天、截图、系统命令执行</p>\n        </div>\n        <div id=\"status\" class=\"status\" role=\"status\" aria-live=\"polite\">就绪</div>\n      </header>\n\n      <section class=\"panel config-panel\">\n        <h2>连接设置</h2>\n        <div class=\"form-grid\">\n          <label>\n            API Base URL（可选）\n            <input id=\"baseUrlInput\" type=\"text\" placeholder=\"留空表示同源，例如 http://127.0.0.1:3000\" />\n          </label>\n          <label>\n            Session ID\n            <input id=\"sessionIdInput\" type=\"text\" placeholder=\"默认自动生成，可手动修改\" />\n          </label>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <main class=\"dashboard-grid\">\n        <section class=\"panel chat-panel\">\n          <div class=\"panel-head\">\n            <h2>双向聊天</h2>\n            <button id=\"clearChatBtn\" type=\"button\" class=\"btn ghost\">清空界面消息</button>\n          </div>\n\n          <div id=\"chatMessages\" class=\"chat-messages\" aria-live=\"polite\"></div>\n\n          <form id=\"chatForm\" class=\"chat-form\">\n            <label class=\"sr-only\" for=\"chatInput\">输入消息</label>\n            <textarea id=\"chatInput\" rows=\"3\" placeholder=\"输入消息，支持 Shift+Enter 换行\"></textarea>\n            <button id=\"sendChatBtn\" type=\"submit\" class=\"btn primary\">发送</button>\n          </form>\n        </section>\n        ...\n      </main>\n    </div>\n    <script type=\"module\" src=\"./js/main.js\"></script>\n  </body>\n</html>\n```\n\n**Target**: Line 44 — `<textarea id=\"chatInput\" rows=\"3\" placeholder=\"输入消息，支持 Shift+Enter 换行\">`\n**Change**: Update placeholder to `请输入对话`\n\n## Section 5 — Existing Tests\n\nNo tests exist for HTML placeholder values (frontend-only static attribute change).\n","structuredPatch":[{"oldStart":87,"oldLines":3,"newStart":87,"newLines":7,"lines":[" ## Section 5 — Existing Tests"," "," No tests exist for HTML placeholder values (frontend-only static attribute change).","+","+## Implementation Log","+Files changed/created: public/index.html","+Key decisions: Single attribute change on textarea#chatInput, from「输入消息，支持 Shift+Enter 换行」to「请输入对话」. No backend, JS, or CSS changes needed. Pre-existing test failures (92) confirmed unrelated to this change."]}],"userModified":false,"replaceAll":false}}
